com.absio.crypto.key

Class IndexedECPublicKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.absio.crypto.key.IndexedECPublicKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexedKey, Serializable, ECKey, ECPublicKey, Key, PublicKey

    public class IndexedECPublicKey
extends Object
implements ECPublicKey
    This class represents a public elliptic curve IndexedKey. The underlying key is an ECPublicKey.
